title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Pat Micheletti, Justin Gaard, Aaron Gleeman
description: Nordo fills in for PA, Pat Micheletti joins to talk Wild Hockey and their win over the Ducks, as well as the NCAA tournament for Hockey and Hoops, Justin Gaard talks Gophers new Head Coach Ben Johnson, we hear the introductory presser, and Aaron Gleeman joins to talk Wolves, and Twins TV rights.
